{"tid":248262,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【有link冇圖】世界第一次睇10週年iPhone嘅最終設計","createTime":"2017-05-18T12:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T07:22:46.000Z","uid":35791,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc33082965e8a3523112025ddb7d52508274b483","tid":248262,"uid":35791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T12:10:25.000Z","msg":"傳蘋果即將推出的新款iPhone 8將最終發布更大變化嘅iPhone。蘋果的新iPhone 7s和iPhone 7s Plus肯定會令人印象深刻的智能手機，但每個人都在等待的是iPhone 8，傳iPhone 8將採用大膽的新設計，將不銹鋼框架夾在2.5D玻璃面。結果應該是無縫的。iPhone 8的面貌預計將推出新的OLED顯示屏，屏幕對身體比率比三星Galaxy S8和Galaxy S8 +管理的83％的比例更令人印象深刻。據報導，這將部分通過轉移設備的內部組件，也可以通過完全刪除iPhone的主頁按鈕來實現。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/201019_708a4f6a9f7f94a316517ba96b8ed34b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F201019_708a4f6a9f7f94a316517ba96b8ed34b.jpg&h=94a6f4f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/201020_812284aaa18c342c212cecaebd667673.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F201020_812284aaa18c342c212cecaebd667673.jpg&h=eaab638c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://codenuts.hk/zh/nuts/2552\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcodenuts.hk%2Fzh%2Fnuts%2F2552&d=07YJri3FF82qzkXABTRKfDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=1be33a16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://codenuts.hk/zh/nuts/2552</a>"},{"pid":"10a53ae418950864331011813adb1aa8e79752c1","tid":248262,"uid":106340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T12:48:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b436fda0077bdf6bae75fc1623c3ec7bdee42efa","tid":248262,"uid":14600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:23:09.000Z","msg":"咁撚厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b80c27d40e79ac041c38af5f9892e29af529bbb","tid":248262,"uid":106302,"like":0,"di